{"tid":1797994,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[感謝黨系列］國資委：今年劃轉國資1.1萬億元人民幣予社保基金","createTime":"2019-12-26T01:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T11:12:05.000Z","uid":288913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a6caa4ed70b79eab698ea10d9890b36a085af8a5","tid":1797994,"uid":288913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T01:14:59.000Z","msg":"中國國資委舉辦央企負責人會議指，今年首11個月中央企業淨利潤按年增長9%，營業收入增長5%，同期投資總額增速達9.4%；又指今年中央企業完成向社保基金劃轉國有股權任務，已劃轉國有資本1.1萬億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n新華社引述會議內容指，截至11月底，央企平均資產負債率按年降低0.1個百分點，剔除有關因素後同口徑下降超過1個百分點，58家企業資產負債率下降，債務風險總體可控在控。首11個月央企研發投入增長24.6%，其中石油石化、鋼鐵、汽車等行業企業研發投入增速逾30%。 <br />\n<br />\n國資委主任郝鵬在會上指，中央企業供給側結構性改革持續深化，2019年央企「壓減」工作提前完成，累計減少法人超過1.4萬戶；「處僵治困」整體工作進度達96%；鋼鐵、煤炭去產能任務全面完成。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499610-20191226.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499610-20191226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFPUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=2af7ba5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499610-20191226.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4fb66da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499610-20191226.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝黨！又將黨企益民眾啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有得分（負）利潤，有份共享（負）淨資產啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304df280e26792b7a5c3db1e598c75d4fd2b05e4","tid":1797994,"uid":258133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T01:18:27.000Z","msg":"［緊急最新］12月26日和你Shop 最新變動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1797777\" 